	dprr:hasNoteText "Plut. Brut. 48.1-5, 51.1-52.3.. Philosopher friend and 'companion of Brutus in all his campaigns'. Present in Brutus' headquarter camp before Philippi, survived the battle, with Brutus when he committed suicide." .
